Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.47,0:02:30.40,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an9}捕捉那交错的视线
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.50,0:02:35.46,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an8}喜欢我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.82,0:02:38.84,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an8}拜托了  Bitter  Tune
